              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/5472faa96cc230f0c6a742c278748e91_7916807034878084978.png",
                "id": "talent30962",
                "key": "Searing Precept",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Searing Precept"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkfire Furnace</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/1cfb4a644ede1096bcf61f228e14be0a_4380761079104067423.png",
                "id": "talent50075",
                "key": "Ominous Star",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ominous Star"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fiery Rebirth</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fiery Rebirth</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached would be defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure the character <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">will not be defeated</span>, and heal them to 4 HP. After this effect is triggered, this character deals +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong></p><p>Certain effects will grant characters an<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.</p><p>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat</span>. (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/241466b9ccdefb6219ef6bf74cd493e2_514740321519811693.png",
                "id": "talent25225",
                "key": "Fiery Rebirth",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fiery Rebirth"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>, deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4525100905009447342.png",
                "id": "talent61948",
                "key": "Darkfire Furnace",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/2cce1877020bad6ed9476a8bb8db436c_4887589208328054219.png",
                "title": "Darkfire Furnace"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_8541099141829379885.png",
                "id": "talent9167",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6571104341758658834.png",
